My favorite thing about CSU so far is the small class sizes, which make it easier to connect with professors and classmates. The tuition is affordable, which helps reduce financial stress while pursuing my degree. I also appreciate that there are more online class options available, especially for working adults like me who need flexibility. Additionally, the school feels similar to a community college, which allows me to stay local without having to move or spend extra money on housing.
